commit.message: feat: selection_meta_key, action_meta_key for easier keybind changing

fix: #712
fix: the last var when setting env variables is not read
fix: --preview-side could be something ytfzf couldnt handle
fix: the default on_no_thumbnail no longer dies so that on_no_thumbnail_<ext> can be called
fix: trim_blank trims too many blanks
feat: add -csi as an alias for -cSI and -cs as an alias for -cS
docs: fix bad html entity in readme
fix: trim_blank does not in fact, trim the blanks
fix: remove extra new line when printing warning about undetermined term size
